data.description: Welcome to this incredible 6 bedrooms, 4 full baths home, with exceptional custom design open kitchen, featuring generous cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, large beautiful island and pantry. Kitchen overlooks to a large family room with stacked stone fireplace. Conveniently located a large bedroom and full bathroom in main level for all your family needs, and  then upstairs we can count with additional 3 bedrooms 2 full baths, where the oversized master bedroom features custom bath with separate shower and tub. Additionally upstairs, large den/family room  that offers year-round enjoyment. I have to mention also the big beautiful basement with so much potential to add living space to the home, which currently has 2 finished rooms and a full bathroom. Basement counts with a separated HVAC system that was installed on 2020.  A lot   space, a lot potential.  Storage and entertainment  at your best !!
